└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

GENERATION SIZES (typical):
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
• Young Gen: 1/3 of heap (default)
  - Eden: ~90% of young gen
  - Survivor: ~10% of young gen (two equal spaces)
• Old Gen: 2/3 of heap
• Large Object Space: separate region
